{"_id":"FDI6wWSbt5BfPa3k","name":"Part Water","content":"<h1>Part Water</h1>\n\t\t\t\t\t<p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<i>Arcane Transmutation/Alteration</i>\n\t\t\t\t\t</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t<table>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tbody><tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>Level:</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>Magic user 6</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>Range:</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>10-ft/level</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>Duration:</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>5 rounds/level</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>Area of Effect:</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>See below</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>Components:</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>V,S,M</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>Casting Time:</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>1 turn</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>Saving Throw:</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>None</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t</tbody></table>\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\tPart Water\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t<p>Except as may be noted above, this spell is identical to the clerical spell <i>part water </i>.</p>","folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"I0IQ9ef7ZhLd66iw":3},"flags":{"scene-packer":{"hash":"b9d450a10aba38ee3f6538846c2aad1dabec3740","sourceId":"JournalEntry.PlygGgVcuRPKRCMm"},"cf":{"id":"temp_7k8wp5wanki","path":"OSRIC-PC#/CF_SEP/Chapter 2: Spells#/CF_SEP/Magic User Spells","color":"#000000","sort":318}}}
{"_id":"FQkBFR0tfjX3kpII","name":"False Trap","content":"<h1>False Trap</h1>\n\t\t\t\t\t<p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<i>Arcane Illusion/Phantasm</i>\n\t\t\t\t\t</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t<table>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tbody><tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>Level:</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>Magic user 2</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>Range:</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>Touch</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>Duration:</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>Permanent</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>Area of Effect:</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>One object</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>Components:</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>V,S,M</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>Casting Time:</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>3 rounds</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>Saving Throw:</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>None</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t</tbody></table>\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\tFalse Trap\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t<p>By means of this spell, the mage weaves an illusion around an object, <b>making it appear trapped to any normal inspection (such as by a thief). Any such examiner has an 80% chance of finding and believing the </b><b><i>false trap </i></b><b>. </b><u>This likelihood decreases by 3% per level of experience of the thief. Furthermore, if a thief attempts to remove the illusory trap, believing it to be real, there is only a 20% likelihood that the illusion will be dispelled or exposed by these efforts. </u>In this case, the thief, seeing the illusion unchanged, will usually conclude that the attempt to remove the \"trap\" has failed. <u>Only one </u><i><u>false trap </u></i><u>may be placed within a 50-ft radius, and if two items bearing this illusion come within 50-ft of each other, both will be dispelled.</u></p>","folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"I0IQ9ef7ZhLd66iw":3},"flags":{"scene-packer":{"hash":"512aa0f1feda497a1315beb936d67630615cc7c3","sourceId":"JournalEntry.FQkBFR0tfjX3kpII"},"cf":{"id":"temp_7k8wp5wanki","path":"OSRIC-PC#/CF_SEP/Chapter 2: Spells#/CF_SEP/Magic User Spells","color":"#000000","sort":241}}}
{"_id":"FW50uV4fpKsKLdJX","name":"Polymorph Self","content":"<h1>Polymorph Self</h1>\n\t\t\t\t\t<p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<i>Arcane Transmutation/Alteration</i>\n\t\t\t\t\t</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t<table>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tbody><tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>Level:</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>Magic user 4</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>Range:</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>Caster</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>Duration:</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>2 turns/level</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>Area of Effect:</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>Caster</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>Components:</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>V</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>Casting Time:</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>3 segments</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>Saving Throw:</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>None</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t</tbody></table>\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\tPolymorph Self\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t<p>This spell enables the magic user to cloak him- or herself in the physical shape of another creature, and to continue shape-shifting at will for the length of the spell's duration. The transformation is of an entirely lesser order than that of <i>polymorph other </i>, <b>incurring no risk of a system shock or of truly becoming the transformed creature. </b>Changing from one shape to another requires only 30 seconds, and <b>when the caster returns to his or her original form (ending the spell) he or she will be healed of [[/roll 1d12]] points of any damage </b>inflicted against the polymorphed forms he or she assumed.</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t<p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<b>The caster can polymorph into forms no smaller than a songbird and no heavier than 2,000 lbs. </b>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<u>Only the movement capabilities of the new form can be used, not its attacks, defences, or other abilities. </u>The magic user can transform him- or herself into a lion, and run as fast as a lion, but his or her claws will do no more damage than a human's soft fists. Similarly, if he or she transforms into a dragon, he or she will have the dragon's ability to fly but no breath weapon. As an orc, he or she would be able to use whatever weapons he or she could use in his original shape, but would lack infravision. <b>The caster retains his or her own hit points and armour class.</b></p>","folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"I0IQ9ef7ZhLd66iw":3},"flags":{"scene-packer":{"hash":"d2187da9ec74202804a42516720259b5336a38fa","sourceId":"JournalEntry.FW50uV4fpKsKLdJX"},"cf":{"id":"temp_7k8wp5wanki","path":"OSRIC-PC#/CF_SEP/Chapter 2: Spells#/CF_SEP/Magic User Spells","color":"#000000","sort":326}}}
{"_id":"FchtrxWrFvitIVxJ","name":"Dispel Evil (Reversible)","content":"<h1>Dispel Evil (Reversible)</h1>\n\t\t\t\t\t<p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<i>Clerical Abjuration</i>\n\t\t\t\t\t</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t<table>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tbody><tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>Level:</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>Cleric 5</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>Range:</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>Touch</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>Duration:</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>1 round/caster level</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>Area of Effect:</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>Creature touched</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>Components:</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>V,S,M</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>Casting Time:</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>8 segments</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>Saving Throw:</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>See below</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t</tbody></table>\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\tDispel Evil\n\t\t\t\t\t\tDispel Good\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t<p>This spell banishes summoned creatures of evil, or those summoned for evil purposes, to their home planes of existence. <u>Although a saving throw negates the spell's banishing effect </u>, <b>any creature that would otherwise have been banished will suffer a penalty of -7 \"to hit\" the caster for the extent of the spell's duration.</b></p>\n\t\t\t\t\t<p>Creatures affected by this spell include, but are certainly not limited to, afreets, demons, devils, genies (either evil or working toward evil purposes under duress), and elementals summoned for evil purposes. The reverse of the spell has the same effects, but upon summoned creatures of good alignment or those summoned for the purposes of good.</p>","folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"I0IQ9ef7ZhLd66iw":3},"flags":{"scene-packer":{"hash":"92a25223401af47ec532ff74635e4bdd7bd8ff5e","sourceId":"JournalEntry.FchtrxWrFvitIVxJ"},"cf":{"id":"temp_65r8ksx2p43","path":"OSRIC-PC#/CF_SEP/Chapter 2: Spells#/CF_SEP/Cleric Spells","color":"#000000","sort":61}}}
{"_id":"Fh3Du2WoXvJqXCmz","name":"Wall of Stone","content":"<h1>Wall of Stone</h1>\n\t\t\t\t\t<p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<i>Arcane Evocation</i>\n\t\t\t\t\t</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t<table>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tbody><tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>Level:</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>Magic user 5</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>Range:</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>5-ft/level</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>Duration:</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>Permanent</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>Area of Effect:</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>20-ft20-ft square/level</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>Components:</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>V,S,M</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>Casting Time:</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>5 segments</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>Saving Throw:</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>None</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t</tbody></table>\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\tWall of Stone\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t<p>When the spell is completed, a <i>wall of stone </i>is called into being, sprouting from existing stone formations. <u>In order for the spell to succeed, there must be existing rock large enough to serve as the anchor on each side of the wall. </u>No rock from the foundation is consumed; the wall's stone is created from nothing, but needs existing rock from which to emerge and with which to meld. The wall itself is one quarter of an inch thick for each level of the magic user and has an area of 20-ft20-ft per caster level. <b>The wall need not be vertical, but must be anchored-a bridge is a good example of a way to create and use a horizontal </b><b><i>wall of stone. </i></b><b><u>The wall may be dispelled, but otherwise has all the characteristics of natural stone.</u></b></p>","folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"I0IQ9ef7ZhLd66iw":3},"flags":{"scene-packer":{"hash":"f37c51cd7142c943d9afce33a88be56a1c2d2e58","sourceId":"JournalEntry.Fh3Du2WoXvJqXCmz"},"cf":{"id":"temp_7k8wp5wanki","path":"OSRIC-PC#/CF_SEP/Chapter 2: Spells#/CF_SEP/Magic User Spells","color":"#000000","sort":379}}}
