{"_id":"LM9SdSWIXTeJCILT","name":"Shatter","content":"<h1>Shatter</h1>\n\t\t\t\t\t<p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<i>Arcane Transmutation/Alteration</i>\n\t\t\t\t\t</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t<table>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tbody><tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>Level:</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>Magic user 2</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>Range:</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>60-ft</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>Duration:</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>Instantaneous</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>Area of Effect:</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>One object</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>Components:</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>V,S,M</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>Casting Time:</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>2 segments</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>Saving Throw:</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>Negates</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t</tbody></table>\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\tShatter\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t<p>This spell causes an item to shatter into pieces. <b>It can affect objects of up to 10 lbs weight per caster level. </b>Only brittle materials are affected by the spell (glass, earthenware, etc.) <u>excluding magical items of any kind. The item is permitted a saving throw against a crushing blow to avoid destruction </u>.</p>","folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"I0IQ9ef7ZhLd66iw":3},"flags":{"scene-packer":{"hash":"68acc10d4f2a80a45565fda40f6272e53e1d6bdb","sourceId":"JournalEntry.LM9SdSWIXTeJCILT"},"cf":{"id":"temp_7k8wp5wanki","path":"OSRIC-PC#/CF_SEP/Chapter 2: Spells#/CF_SEP/Magic User Spells","color":"#000000","sort":347}}}
{"_id":"Ll3YGXtTzroymIQC","name":"Shadow Door","content":"<h1>Shadow Door</h1>\n\t\t\t\t\t<p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<i>Phantasmal Illusion</i>\n\t\t\t\t\t</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t<table>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tbody><tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>Level:</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>Illusionist 5</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>Range:</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>10-ft</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>Duration:</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>1 round/level</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>Area of Effect:</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>Magic door</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>Components:</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>S</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>Casting Time:</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>2 segments</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>Saving Throw:</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>None</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t</tbody></table>\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\tShadow Door\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t<p>With a mystical gesture, the illusionist creates an illusory door (either in a wall or free-standing). <b>If the illusionist steps through, he or she disappears from sight and may go where he or she pleases. If anyone else opens the door, they will perceive a small empty room. </b>The caster's invisibility after passing through the <i>shadow door </i>is particularly powerful and <u>cannot be seen by use of detect invisibility, although he or she can be seen with more powerful divination magic.</u></p>","folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"I0IQ9ef7ZhLd66iw":3},"flags":{"scene-packer":{"hash":"1f8c9a2d3985841d8a98a4b9838e8515796009c8","sourceId":"JournalEntry.Ll3YGXtTzroymIQC"},"cf":{"id":"temp_7fkpa5jvvmt","path":"OSRIC-PC#/CF_SEP/Chapter 2: Spells#/CF_SEP/Illusionist Spells","color":"#000000","sort":442}}}
{"_id":"LpohGcWMNbhAREp9","name":"Clenched Fist","content":"<h1>Clenched Fist</h1>\n\t\t\t\t\t<p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<i>Arcane Evocation</i>\n\t\t\t\t\t</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t<table>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tbody><tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>Level:</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>Magic user 8</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>Range:</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>5-ft/level</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>Duration:</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>1 round/level</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>Area of Effect:</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>Enchanted hand</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>Components:</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>V,S,M</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>Casting Time:</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>8 segments</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>Saving Throw:</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>None</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t</tbody></table>\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\tClenched Fist\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t<p>As with the other hand spells, <i>clenched fist </i>evokes a magical hand, but in this case <b>the hand is always at least as large as a giant's and is curled into a fist rather than held open. The clenched fist strikes one of the magic user's enemies per round, never missing, </b>for so long as the caster concentrates upon it. <b>No other activity is possible while concentrating </b>, and breaking the caster's concentration ends the spell. <b>The fist rolls a [[/roll 1d20]] to determine damage (it hits automatically): on a roll of 1-12, the fist deals [[/roll 1d6]] hp of damage; on a 13-15, it deals [[/roll 2d6]] hit points, on a roll of 16-19 it deals [[/roll 3d6]] hit points and stuns the opponent for one round, and on a roll of 20+ it deals [[/roll 4d6]] hit points and stuns the opponent for 3 rounds. If the opponent has already been stunned, the [[/roll 1d20]] roll receives a +4 bonus. </b>As with the other hand spells, the hand has as many hit points as the caster's full hit points.</p>","folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"I0IQ9ef7ZhLd66iw":3},"flags":{"scene-packer":{"hash":"2a6caae7e2501c4c6e66d84dcc52dc4f1c37b382","sourceId":"JournalEntry.LpohGcWMNbhAREp9"},"cf":{"id":"temp_7k8wp5wanki","path":"OSRIC-PC#/CF_SEP/Chapter 2: Spells#/CF_SEP/Magic User Spells","color":"#000000","sort":208}}}
{"_id":"M7uqHBcnF0pmQKFv","name":"Clairvoyance","content":"<h1>Clairvoyance</h1>\n\t\t\t\t\t<p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<i>Arcane Divination</i>\n\t\t\t\t\t</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t<table>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tbody><tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>Level:</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>Magic user 3</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>Range:</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>See below</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>Duration:</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>1 round/level</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>Area of Effect:</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>See below</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>Components:</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>V,S,M</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>Casting Time:</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>3 segments</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>Saving Throw:</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>None</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t</tbody></table>\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\tClairvoyance\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t<p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<i>Clairvoyance </i>, together with <i>clairaudience </i>, is one of the classic \"scrying\" spells-spells that <b>allow the caster to extend his or her perception and senses far into the distance to spy upon enemies and scout locations. </b><i>Clairvoyance </i>is a means of seeing events in a distant location. There is no effective limit to the spell's range, but <b>the location must either be familiar to the caster or be obvious, such as the top floor inside a tower the caster can see, or just beyond a dungeon door.</b></p>\n\t\t\t\t\t<p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<u>The spell cannot penetrate metal; sheets of any type of metal between the caster and the target area will prevent the magic user from being able to scry upon the area. </u>The caster will be able to hear sounds in a 10-ft radius of the spell's focal point even if the area is dark. If the area is not dark, the caster will be able to see as if he or she were standing at the spell's focal point, for a normal distance but in all directions at once (for the vision is in his or her mind's eye).</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t<p>The spell cannot be used to scry across planes of existence; it is limited to locations in the same plane in which it is cast.</p>","folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"I0IQ9ef7ZhLd66iw":3},"flags":{"scene-packer":{"hash":"e1962d4812133f36e79dff89fe739dfe9dd106eb","sourceId":"JournalEntry.M7uqHBcnF0pmQKFv"},"cf":{"id":"temp_7k8wp5wanki","path":"OSRIC-PC#/CF_SEP/Chapter 2: Spells#/CF_SEP/Magic User Spells","color":"#000000","sort":207}}}
{"_id":"M82P0ggaswcvkvUQ","name":"Emotion","content":"<h1>Emotion</h1>\n\t\t\t\t\t<p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<i>Phantasmal Enchantment/Charm</i>\n\t\t\t\t\t</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t<table>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tbody><tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>Level:</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>Illusionist 4</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>Range:</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>10-ft/level</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>Duration:</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>Until concentration ceases</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>Area of Effect:</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>Up to 40-ft40-ft</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>Components:</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>V,S</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>Casting Time:</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>4 segments</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>Saving Throw:</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>Negates</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t</tbody></table>\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\tEmotion\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t<p>By casting this spell, the illusionist is able to instil others with one of four powerful emotions, each with a different effect, as described below:</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t<p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<i>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<u>Fear: </u>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</i>If the illusionist chooses to instil fear, <b>the spell's effect is similar to that of the </b><b><i>fear </i></b><b>spell, </b>but <u>with a -2 penalty applied to saving throws.</u></p>\n\t\t\t\t\t<p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<i>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<u>Hate: </u>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</i>If the illusionist instils hate, <b>the targets gain a +2 to saving throws, attacks, and damage.</b></p>\n\t\t\t\t\t<p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<i>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<u>Hopelessness: </u>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</i>The illusionist causes despair in the target creatures, <b>who will wander sadly away or surrender in the face of a challenge such as a combat.</b></p>\n\t\t\t\t\t<p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<i>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<u>Rage: </u>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</i>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<b>Creatures affected by rage attack at +1, gain a damage bonus of +3, and gain a bonus of 5 temporary hit points. </b>Temporary hit points are lost first if the creature incurs damage. <b>The affected creature will not willingly retreat from any combat or any opponent.</b></p>","folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"I0IQ9ef7ZhLd66iw":3},"flags":{"scene-packer":{"hash":"ce473c4b048339f30ad8c2a4318486093fcf2552","sourceId":"JournalEntry.M82P0ggaswcvkvUQ"},"cf":{"id":"temp_7fkpa5jvvmt","path":"OSRIC-PC#/CF_SEP/Chapter 2: Spells#/CF_SEP/Illusionist Spells","color":"#000000","sort":410}}}
{"_id":"MJg54AZWQ9JFRXfD","name":"Minor Creation","content":"<h1>Minor Creation</h1>\n\t\t\t\t\t<p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<i>Phantasmal Transmutation/Alteration</i>\n\t\t\t\t\t</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t<table>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tbody><tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>Level:</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>Illusionist 4</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>Range:</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>Touch</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>Duration:</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>6 turns/level</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>Area of Effect:</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>1 cubic-ft/level</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>Components:</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>V,S,M</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>Casting Time:</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>1 turn</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>Saving Throw:</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>None</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t</tbody></table>\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\tMinor Creation\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t<p>With a small piece of material, the caster may use this spell to create an object made of that same material. <u>The base material cannot be alive and must come from a plant. </u>Thus, within the caster's limits on the item's volume, he or she could create a basket from a piece of straw, a door or club from a splinter of wood, a cloak from a piece of wool, etc. The item exists only for the duration of the spell.</p>","folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"I0IQ9ef7ZhLd66iw":3},"flags":{"scene-packer":{"hash":"4039cbd5fa579868d078a9dfb6940c8109809dc6","sourceId":"JournalEntry.MJg54AZWQ9JFRXfD"},"cf":{"id":"temp_7fkpa5jvvmt","path":"OSRIC-PC#/CF_SEP/Chapter 2: Spells#/CF_SEP/Illusionist Spells","color":"#000000","sort":428}}}
