{"_id":"ZGtl3Ravp4bSobGV","name":"Blindness","content":"<h1>Blindness</h1>\n\t\t\t\t\t<p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<i>Phantasmal Illusion</i>\n\t\t\t\t\t</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t<table>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tbody><tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>Level:</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>Illusionist 2</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>Range:</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>30-ft</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>Duration:</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>Permanent</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>Area of Effect:</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>One creature</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>Components:</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>V,S</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>Casting Time:</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>2 segments</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>Saving Throw:</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>Negates</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t</tbody></table>\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\tBlindness\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t<p>This spell causes the subject to become blind, but causes no damage to the eyes themselves. <b>The effect cannot be removed by any spell that restores physical health (such as a healing spell, cure disease, etc), </b><u>but may be dispelled normally. The caster can end the condition at will.</u></p>","folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"I0IQ9ef7ZhLd66iw":3},"flags":{"scene-packer":{"hash":"0b5e150288cbda39cf5db37ddb459dbc1ff7d67b","sourceId":"JournalEntry.ZGtl3Ravp4bSobGV"},"cf":{"id":"temp_7fkpa5jvvmt","path":"OSRIC-PC#/CF_SEP/Chapter 2: Spells#/CF_SEP/Illusionist Spells","color":"#000000","sort":391}}}
