{"_id":"n5JR2iA9gWN7SMBb","name":"Spectral Force","content":"<h1>Spectral Force</h1>\n\t\t\t\t\t<p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<i>Phantasmal Illusion</i>\n\t\t\t\t\t</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t<table>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tbody><tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>Level:</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>Illusionist 3</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>Range:</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>60-ft+10-ft/level</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>Duration:</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>See below</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>Area of Effect:</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>40-ft40-ft square+10-ft10-ft square/level</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>Components:</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>V,S,M</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>Casting Time:</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>3 segments</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>Saving Throw:</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>See below</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t</tbody></table>\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\tSpectral Force\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t<p>This spell functions in the same manner as <i>improved phantasmal force, </i>but it is a more powerful evocation of the same magic. <b>The illusionist can include sounds, smells, and heat (or cold) into the illusion, making it very believable. </b>The spectral force can linger for 3 rounds after the illusionist ceases to concentrate upon it.</p>","folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"I0IQ9ef7ZhLd66iw":3},"flags":{"scene-packer":{"hash":"8b7cb86d1899b25fd0ab0c15a510998550d684b6","sourceId":"JournalEntry.n5JR2iA9gWN7SMBb"},"cf":{"id":"temp_7fkpa5jvvmt","path":"OSRIC-PC#/CF_SEP/Chapter 2: Spells#/CF_SEP/Illusionist Spells","color":"#000000","sort":445}}}
{"_id":"n62qXjynaC9TaKh5","name":"Charm Monster","content":"<h1>Charm Monster</h1>\n\t\t\t\t\t<p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<i>Arcane Enchantment/Charm</i>\n\t\t\t\t\t</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t<table>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tbody><tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>Level:</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>Magic user 4</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>Range:</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>60-ft</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>Duration:</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>See below</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>Area of Effect:</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>See below</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>Components:</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>V,S</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>Casting Time:</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>4 segments</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>Saving Throw:</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>Negates</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t</tbody></table>\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\tCharm Monster\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t<p>This spell operates as <i>charm person </i>does, but can affect any living creature; possibly more than one, depending on the monsters' level value. See the chart below:</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t<table>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tbody><tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<b>Level value of monsters</b>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<b>Number affected</b>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<b>Chance/week to break enchantment</b>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>Level 1</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>[[/roll 2d4]]</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>5%</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>Level 2</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>[[/roll 1d4]]</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>10%</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>Level 3</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>[[/roll 1d2]]</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>15%</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>Level 4</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>1</td>\