rademark of WOTC or any other party is unauthorized, inadvertent, and is not intended to infringe upon the intellectual property rights of such parties.</p>\n<p>Nothing in this document is to be construed as legal advice. For legal questions you should retain a solicitor or attorney to advise you.</p>\n<p><strong>FOR FREE UPDATES, ERRATA AND OTHER OSRIC SUPPORT, VISIT:</strong></p>\n<p>http://www.knights-n-knaves.com/osric</p>","folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"I0IQ9ef7ZhLd66iw":3},"flags":{"scene-packer":{"hash":"2a869f274ae699ee34441b06b833f4ce01afbbc6","sourceId":"JournalEntry.xCKdD25gnYyD0kwA"},"cf":{"id":"temp_e2nju8wswju","path":"OSRIC-PC#/CF_SEP/OSRIC#/CF_SEP/OSRIC Cover","color":"#000000","sort":2}}}
{"_id":"xIVW0OHOERfgxqpt","name":"Deafness","content":"<h1>Deafness</h1>\n\t\t\t\t\t<p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<i>Phantasmal Illusion</i>\n\t\t\t\t\t</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t<table>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tbody><tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>Level:</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>Illusionist 2</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>Range:</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>60-ft</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>Duration:</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>Permanent</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>Area of Effect:</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>One creature</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>Components:</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>V,S,M</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>Casting Time:</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>2 segments</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>Saving Throw:</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>Negates</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t</tbody></table>\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\tDeafness\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t<p>This spell is similar to the illusionist's <i>blindness </i>spell, but causes deafness. <u>The effect is permanent until removed by dispel magic, though it can be removed by the caster at any time.</u></p>","folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"I0IQ9ef7ZhLd66iw":3},"flags":{"scene-packer":{"hash":"fe67c98f62195814f289d930171f6f6a72ca9352","sourceId":"JournalEntry.xIVW0OHOERfgxqpt"},"cf":{"id":"temp_7fkpa5jvvmt","path":"OSRIC-PC#/CF_SEP/Chapter 2: Spells#/CF_SEP/Illusionist Spells","color":"#000000","sort":402}}}
{"_id":"xIgtSI0YNmBBSCYm","name":"Light (Reversible)","content":"<h1>Light (Reversible)</h1>\n\t\t\t\t\t<p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<i>Clerical Transmutation/Alteration</i>\n\t\t\t\t\t</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t<table>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tbody><tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>Level:</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>Cleric 1</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>Range:</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>120-ft</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>Duration:</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>6 turns+1 turn/caster level (half for darkness)</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>Area of Effect:</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>20-ft radius globe</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>Components:</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>V,S</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>Casting Time:</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>4 segments</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>Saving Throw:</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>See below</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t</tbody></table>\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\tLight\n\t\t\t\t\t\tDarkness\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t<p>The <i>light </i>spell creates a globe of light 20-ft in radius, centered upon whatever spot or object the caster indicates at the time of casting (including a location in thin air). The caster may extinguish the magical light at any time. The reverse of the spell, <i>darkness </i>, creates an area of utter darkness just as the <i>light </i>spell creates light, with the only distinction being that the <i>darkness </i>spell has half the duration of a <i>light </i>spell. <u>If either spell is cast upon a living creature, the creature is entitled to a saving throw (success indicating that the spell affects the area just behind the creature) </u>. <b>A </b><b><i>light </i></b><b>spell cast upon a creature's eyes will blind it for the spell's duration, causing it a penalty of -4 on all rolls \"to hit\" if sight is its primary sense. </b>The <i>light </i>spell remains stationary if it was not originally cast upon a movable object or creature (in which case the target will bring the illumination with it as it moves).</p>","folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"I0IQ9ef7ZhLd66iw":3},"flags":{"scene-packer":{"hash":"4df2efa86585a6441856e99cde553a21d7341e71","sourceId":"JournalEntry.xIgtSI0YNmBBSCYm"},"cf":{"id":"temp_65r8ksx2p43","path":"OSRIC-PC#/CF_SEP/Chapter 2: Spells#/CF_SEP/Cleric Spells","color":"#000000","sort":77}}}
{"_id":"xlivuAZMEdc96qPb","name":"Anti-Magic Shell","content":"<h1>Anti-Magic Shell</h1>\n\t\t\t\t\t<p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<i>Arcane Abjuration</i>\n\t\t\t\t\t</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t<table>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tbody><tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>Level:</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>Magic user 6</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>Range:</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>Caster</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>Duration:</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>1 turn/level</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>Area of Effect:</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>5-ft radius/level globe</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>Components:</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>V,S</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>Casting Time:</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>1 segment</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>Saving Throw:</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>None</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t</tbody></table>\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\tAnti-Magic Shell\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t<p>An <i>anti-magic shell </i>is a bubble of space around the magic user that completely prevents all magic from operating within its confines. <u>Spell effects do not enter or function within the shell, providing the caster with complete protection from gaze attacks, hostile spells, and even the entrance of conjured or summoned creatures into his or her vicinity. </u>The drawback of an anti-magic shell, of course, is that <b>the caster him- or herself cannot cast spells or avail him- or herself of magic items while inside. Magic weapons, armour, and the like do not gain their bonuses or abilities while inside the shell, but would still function as non-magical weapons or armour.</b></p>","folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"I0IQ9ef7ZhLd66iw":3},"flags":{"scene-packer":{"hash":"0565c2ddf360bd7f2c303dac55f92d4322d3706d","sourceId":"JournalEntry.xlivuAZMEdc96qPb"},"cf":{"id":"temp_7k8wp5wanki","path":"OSRIC-PC#/CF_SEP/Chapter 2: Spells#/CF_SEP/Magic User Spells","color":"#000000","sort":196}}}
{"_id":"xy9RSU6BSvX83t4G","name":"Augury","content":"<h1>Augury</h1>\n\t\t\t\t\t<p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<i>Clerical Divination</i>\n\t\t\t\t\t</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t<table>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tbody><tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>Level:</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>Cleric 2</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>Range:</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>Caster</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>Duration:</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>Instantaneous</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>Area of Effect:</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>Caster</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>Components:</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>V,S,M</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>Casting Time:</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>2 rounds</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>Saving Throw:</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>None</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t</tbody></table>\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\tAugury\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t<p>Casting an <i>augury </i>allows the cleric to discern minor omens, indications of what might be in the future. The spell requires a focal point that will allow the omens to manifest-a set of sticks made from dragon's bone or gold is the most common focus for the spell. It is possible to derive omens from tea leaves, but a pearl worth 100 gp must be crushed into the infusion. The divination power of an <i>augury </i>is not strong; <b>it will only gather omens from the pattern of the next 3 turns (30 minutes), and can only indicate whether a future action will result in weal or woe to the party. The base chance for correctly interpreting the omens is 70% plus an additional 1% per level of the caster.</b></p>","folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"I0IQ9ef7ZhLd66iw":3},"flags":{"scene-packer":{"hash":"309d3732eb51f7bc2735c28b5e23983624901285","sourceId":"JournalEntry.xy9RSU6BSvX83t4G"},"cf":{"id":"temp_65r8ksx2p43","path":"OSRIC-PC#/CF_SEP/Chapter 2: Spells#/CF_SEP/Cleric Spells","color":"#000000","sort":41}}}
{"_id":"yCKcR0U65feIazyy","name":"Turn Wood","content":"<h1>Turn Wood</h1>\n\t\t\t\t\t<p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<i>Druidic Transmutation/Alteration</i>\n\t\t\t\t\t</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t<table>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tbody><tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>Level:</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>Druid 6</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>Range:</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>0</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>Duration:</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>4 rounds/caster level</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>Area of Effect:</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>120-ft wide path, 20-ft long/caster level</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>Components:</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>V,S,M</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>Casting Time:</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>8 segments</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>Saving Throw:</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>None</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t</tbody></table>\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\tTurn Wood\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t<p>At the completion of this spell, the druid holds his or her palm outstretched, and <b>with the final word of the spell a tremendous burst of power rolls forth, forcing back all wooden objects. Even very large wooden structures that are not affixed to the ground will be affected, although objects fixed to the ground will manage to withstand the spell's awesome power. </b>A sapling-sized or smaller piece of wood will splinter and break even if it is firmly affixed. <b>The druid need not concentrate on maintaining the waves of force and cannot change the direction of the flow </b>of eldritch power once it is set.</p>","folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"I0IQ9ef7ZhLd66iw":3},"flags":{"scene-packer":{"hash":"bb0e8e8c4fc7c73c3a6e64d39293963a3d1b6119","sourceId":"JournalEntry.yCKcR0U65feIazyy"},"cf":{"id":"temp_w788fmzkfq","path":"OSRIC-PC#/CF_SEP/Chapter 2: Spells#/CF_SEP/Druid Spells","color":"#000000","sort":185}}}
{"_id":"yECmXwyxEmqF6Lgo","name":"Regenerate (Reversible)","content":"<h1>Regenerate (Reversible)</h1>\n\t\t\t\t\t<p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<i>Clerical Necromancy</i>\n\t\t\t\t\t</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t<table>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tbody><tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>Level:</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>Cleric 7</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>Range:</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>Touch</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>Duration:</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>Instantaneous</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>Area of Effect:</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>One creature</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>Components:</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>V,S,M</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>Casting Time:</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>3 rounds</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>Saving Throw:</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>None</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t</tbody></table>\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\tRegenerate\n\t\t\t\t\t\tWither\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t<p>The powerful <i>regeneration </i>spell causes <b>severed body parts to reattach themselves in a single round, or to regrow within 2-8 turns. The spell's reverse causes a touched appendage to wither and fall away to dust within 2-8 turns. </b><u>A successful attack must be made in order to cast the spell upon an unwilling victim </u>, but the victim does not also receive a saving throw.</p>","folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"I0IQ9ef7ZhLd66iw":3},"flags":{"scene-packer":{"hash":"6590ff217eae680871b04efdfe951c1c6ad7340d","sourceId":"JournalEntry.yECmXwyxEmqF6Lgo"},"cf":{"id":"temp_65r8ksx2p43","path":"OSRIC-PC#/CF_SEP/Chapter 2: Spells#/CF_SEP/Cleric Spells","color":"#000000","sort":89}}}
{"_id":"yM2GSlnlXVVqDzcQ","name":"Mending","content":"<h1>Mending</h1>\n\t\t\t\t\t<p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<i>Arcane Transmutation/Alteration</i>\n\t\t\t\t\t</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t<table>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tbody><tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>Level:</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>Magic user 1</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>Range:</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>30-ft</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>Duration:</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>Instantaneous</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>Area of Effect:</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>One object</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>Components:</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>V,S,M</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>Casting Time:</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>1 segment</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>Saving Throw:</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>None</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t</tbody></table>\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\tMending\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t<p>This spell repairs small breaks or tears in an object. It can weld together broken metallic objects, such as a chain link or a broken dagger, rejoin a broken bottle, and repair holes in leather or cloth, for example. <u>The spell does not repair magic items in any way that would restore or affect their magical qualities.</u></p>","folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"I0IQ9ef7ZhLd66iw":3},"flags":{"scene-packer":{"hash":"48fdd19534445126d14523da7d3eafe39322f9d6","sourceId":"JournalEntry.yM2GSlnlXVVqDzcQ"},"cf":{"id":"temp_7k8wp5wanki","path":"OSRIC-PC#/CF_SEP/Chapter 2: Spells#/CF_SEP/Magic User Spells","color":"#000000","sort":303}}}
{"_id":"yOBSp5JGQMhaXETm","name":"Speak with Plants","content":"<h1>Speak with Plants</h1>\n\t\t\t\t\t<p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<i>Clerical Transmutation/Alteration</i>\n\t\t\t\t\t</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t<table>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tbody><tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>Level:</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>Cleric 4</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>Range:</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>Caster</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>Duration:</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>1 round/caster level</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>Area of Effect:</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>Caster</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>Components:</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>V,S,M</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>Casting Time:</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>1 turn</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>Saving Throw:</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>None</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t</tbody></table>\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\tSpeak with Plants\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t<p>The cleric becomes able to hold converse with living plant matter. He or she may pose questions and understand the answers given, although any conclusions or opinions the plant provides will be based on the plant's level of intelligence. Even a normal plant, however, will be able to convey information about events that have transpired near it. <b>If the plants are capable of motion, it will be possible for the cleric to persuade them into a course of action, such as drawing aside to allow passage, or even attacking an enemy citadel.</b></p>","folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"I0IQ9ef7ZhLd66iw":3},"flags":{"scene-packer":{"hash":"fd460b3cd0a30415fae9219c51e2fd34d3406db5","sourceId":"JournalEntry.yOBSp5JGQMhaXETm"},"cf":{"id":"temp_65r8ksx2p43","path":"OSRIC-PC#/CF_SEP/Chapter 2: Spells#/CF_SEP/Cleric Spells","color":"#000000","sort":103}}}
